<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>WELCOME TO CLASS ANANDA ALWY FAWWAZY</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b,#334155);
    color:white;
    min-height:100vh;
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* Animasi Background */
body::before{
    content:"";
    position:fixed;
    width:200%;
    height:200%;
    background:
    radial-gradient(circle,#38bdf8 2px,transparent 2px);
    background-size:50px 50px;
    animation: moveBg 15s linear infinite;
    opacity:0.15;
}

@keyframes moveBg{
    from{transform:translate(0,0);}
    to{transform:translate(-100px,-100px);}
}

.container{
    text-align:center;
    padding:60px 20px;
    position:relative;
    z-index:1;
}

h1{
    font-size:3rem;
    color:#38bdf8;
    text-shadow:0 0 20px #38bdf8;
    animation: glow 2s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes glow{
    from{
        text-shadow:0 0 10px #38bdf8;
    }
    to{
        text-shadow:0 0 30px #38bdf8,
                     0 0 50px #38bdf8;
    }
}

.subtitle{
    margin-top:15px;
    font-size:1.2rem;
    animation: fadeIn 3s ease;
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
    from{
        opacity:0;
        transform:translateY(30px);
    }
    to{
        opacity:1;
        transform:translateY(0);
    }
}

.card{
    max-width:900px;
    margin:40px auto;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:20px;
    box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.card h2{
    color:#60a5fa;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

ul{
    text-align:left;
    margin-left:25px;
    line-height:2;
}

.footer{
    margin-top:30px;
    color:#cbd5e1;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:12px 25px;
    background:#38bdf8;
    color:black;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-weight:bold;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    transform:scale(1.1);
    box-shadow:0 0 20px #38bdf8;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>WELCOME TO CLASS</h1>
    <h1>ANANDA ALWY FAWWAZY</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
        Belajar HTML, CSS, dan Dasar Pengembangan Website
    </p>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>📚 Materi yang Dipelajari</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Struktur Dasar HTML</li>
            <li>Heading dan Paragraf</li>
            <li>Bold, Italic, dan Underline</li>
            <li>Menampilkan Gambar</li>
            <li>Membuat Link</li>
            <li>Bullet Point dan Number List</li>
            <li>Membuat Tabel</li>
            <li>Membuat Formulir</li>
            <li>CSS untuk Desain Website</li>
            <li>Animasi Website Modern</li>
        </ul>

        <a href="#" class="btn">Mulai Belajar</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2026 - Class Ananda Alwy Fawwazy
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
